Tata, d tawacult n iɣersiwen imraraden yeṭṭafaren adu-tfesna n tezyagurin deg tfesna n tmeskebrin.
Amayas d yiwet n telmest yettekkin di twacult n tserɣuda, Yettwassen s tizli-ynes ur yezmir ula d yiwen n iɣersiwen ad tyaweṭ maca tazla ayi tettmagar-it-id tesdedt d telweɣt n tfekka
Messasat d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Alismataceae.

Awamɣil neɣ Azara d tawacult meqqren n iɣersiwen yettidiren deg Tefriqt d Asya, Dɣa aɣersiw-a d talmest yettwaggzen s wengar s usrag n wegmar id t-yeṭṭafaren i tukksa n yicc-is yettusxedmen deg tesnujya aladɣa deg tmurt n Ccinwa
Abanɣu, d aɣersiw asuṭṭaḍ, yedder deg Tefriqt.
Agrur, Llan wid is yeqqaren Tanqelt, d aseklu id yessemɣayen agummu n tabexsist, Tettwaẓu deg usamar alemmas d Turkya, Tamurt n Leqbayel, tewwed ar Kalifurnya akk d Aneẓẓul n Turuft.
Afernan neɣ Tiggit neɣ Abucic d talmest n isekla yeṭṭafaren tawsit n udren deg twacult n Tazzant.
Asɣeṛsif d yiwet n tewsit n isekla yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tsemlalin d tfesna n temderranin

Aberru neɣ Ajṛad d aburɣas yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tserdefriwin dges ugar n 20,000 n telmas yettidiren deg yidgan yemgaraden deg umadal, Aberru iga d yiwet n telmast n yebẓaẓ ilan iṭarren udfiren ttallen-t i wenttag anda tezmer ad tentteg azal n 20 n tikkal n teɣzi n tfekka-ynes
Timejja d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Lamiaceae.
Tiwinas neɣ Asɣab d talmest n yemɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult Tamersint.
Ḥeb leḥlawa d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Apiaceae.
Iberdeɣyal d tawacult n yijqiwen yebṭan ɣef 27 n tewsitin d ugar n 150 n telmas.
Wirzan d yiwen n uɣersiw amseksum yeṭṭafaren tawsit n isirru deg twacult n tedɣaɣatin, yettidir deg Tefriqt akk d kra n izegnan n Asya am Blucistan d usamar n Iṛan d tzunegzirt taserɣint.

Tiwukin d aylal aselkiw iy ssermaden deg iṭ yeggunin s waṭas ɣef tanila n tmesliwt yuddsen s waṭas d wallen-is timeqranin id yettaken timeẓriwt igerzen deg iṭ i wegmar n tgemrawin am iɣeṛdayen d igtal
Azuɣnennay neɣ Asaylal neɣ Aɣyul n yiṭ neɣ imceɣlel d aɣersiw amsuṭaṭ amyiwen yettferfiren.
Anẓid amaylal d yiwen n ukerdis dges azal n 50 telmas n tenẓidin ṭṭafaren-t yakk tafesna n temseɣẓaẓ

Tazɣuda neɣ Aɣeṛda yesɣaren d yiwet n telmest n temseɣẓaẓ yeṭṭafaren tawacult n iɣeṛdayen, Tazɣuda meqqer s imik ɣef uɣeṛda n wexxam == Aglam == Talmest-a d tin ilan Tafekka tazrgrart d usallaf ɣezzifen, Teɣzi n tfekka n tezɣuda d tin yettawṭen seg 8 ar 11 cm.
Tafuri d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n euphorbiaceae.
Taksa d awal yettusxedmen i yiɣersiwen imegruden deg imezziren i wfaras n uyefki d weksum d taduṭṭ, Maca iwuzaṭ d imezziren n iselman ur ddin ara deg usismel-a
Awdan d aɣersiw asuṭad amseksum yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tserɣuda, Awdan yettusismel seg tserɣuda meẓẓiyen maca d netta yakk i d ameqran deg-sent, Tazla ynes d tin yudsen ar wagla n uzdal

Tawurta n Kanada d aɣersiw amseksum yeṭṭafaren tawsit n twurta deg twacult n tserɣuda, Yettili-d s waṭas i twurta n Urasya ɣer tfesniwt anda imusnawen ttwalin d akken-itent d yiwet n telmest, Maca tawurta n Kanada tettemcabi i twurta tazeggaɣt deg kra n iylan ugar n twurta n Urasya
Tafduxt d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n tmejjirt.
Tabuzegrayezt d tawsit n yijqiwen meẓẓiyen yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tbuzegrayzin.
Uccen neɣ Uccen uṛɣan d aɣersiw amseksum n tuccenin yeṭṭafaren tawacult n Taydiyyin.
Tifirest neɣ Ifires d talmest n yemɣan yṭṭafaren tawsit n ifires deg twacult tanejjikt

Ilef d aɣersiw asuṭṭad yeṭṭafaren tawsit n telfatin yettidir deg Tefrikt Uruppa d Asya, Dɣa llan-t telmas d timegrudin iw faras n weksum d tmugri n weglim == Aglam == Ilef d aɣersiw amufay azuran yerna yuddes, ila uglan meẓẓiyen ffɣen-d seg yimi-s yerna ɣɣaren-asen timeɣlin.

Alɣem neɣ Alɣem aserɣin d tawsit n iɣersiwen yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tleɣmatin deg tfesna n tsenfednin, Ar tura ur yittwassen uẓar neɣ tamurt taẓaṛant n welɣem maca llan imusnawen id yeqqaren d akken-it yekka-d seg tzunegzirt taserɣint
Agayal d talmest n yizgaren yeṭṭafaren tawsit n ufunas deg twacult n tfunasiyin
Ijqiwen, d yiwet n tfesna tameqrant s waṭas n iylalen dgi yettwaqqen ar ɣures Azgen n telmas n iylalen s wazal n 5400 n telmas
Ajilban n yetbiren d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Fabaceae.
Taferzizt neɣ Tiẓurin n wuccen neɣ Blideɣ
Ṣibus d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Poaceae.
Tibiwt d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Ranunculaceae.
Tasulla d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n fabaceae.
Timerẓuga d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n westeraceae.
Tawelman neɣ Tulma d tawsit n yimɣan isaɣuren yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tetriyyin.

Tisenfednin d tafesna n iɣersiwen imesfednayen maca tetteddu ɣef snat n tfednin timeqranin, Deg tfesna ayyi llan-t temsuṭṭad timeqranin am uɣelmi d tleɣmatin d ufunas d tilmas n iden am umdeɣ d yilef d udad d izerzer
Tigigit d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n caryophyllaceae.
Iferr n wudi d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Primulaceae.
Tinifsanin d ad-adur amɣaw yeṭṭafaren adur n temdudferratin n tgezmi n imɣan igratyen, Dɣa Tinifsanin d imɣan imezdayen yellan s waṭas yakk deg tgelda n yimɣan
Iskimen neɣ Iskim neɣ Izikem

Timesdurifsan d adras amɣaw yeṭṭafaren adu-stirf n temsifsan deg ustirf n temdudferratin, Adras-a yettgi-d yiwet gar snat n tegrawin yellan deg temsifsan, Dɣa imɣan imsifsan sdurayen neɣ teffren ifsan-nsen s agensu n ugummu imi seg iylan-a id yekka yesm-is

column3: Tileɣmatin n yellu, yettwassen daɣen s «Tagmart n nnbi», Udayen ɣɣaren-as: «alɣem n Sliman» d tafesna n ibureɣsen igebren seg 15 n twaculin d 430 n tewsitin d ugar n 2400 n telmas Igmamen n twacult-a d wid yettidiren deg yideggan n yinezwa yemnummsen d imezzayen, Amur ameqqran seg telmas-is d tid yeṭṭafaren tawacult n talɣemt n yelluSeg gar n tenfiwin d ibuɣaṛ n telɣemt n yellu d učči-ines i ibureɣsen ayen yeǧǧan ad tekkes aṭas n tillicin yettmagaren imuzar adɣa ajṛad.Izeɣnunnay d tzermemmuyin gam d angir ameqqran n telɣemt n yellu == Tinnagrawt == Adu-twacult n Mantodea tennulfa-d deg useggas n 1838 sɣur n umesburɣes n Terjuntint Conrado Burmeister == Asemmili == Igmamen n telɣemt n yellu d wid ilan ixef s talɣa n ukeṛdas, ma d allen myuggagent yerna hraw-it, dɣa anecta d ayen i d-yettaken tajumma meqqren i wsekkud d tmuɣli.
Teyfuzzel d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n txaceae.
Tiɛfaṛt d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n tnejjikt.
Aɣsi bu-wazag d yiwet n telmest n temseksumin yeṭṭafaren tawacult n taydiyyin.

Tazermemmuyt d adu-tfesna n temraradin yeṭṭafaren asmil n tzermeskebrin deg wadur n temzikrin Tizermemmuyin d timraradin yettaken aẓaṛ neɣ i d-yettilin i yizerman yerna llant kra n telmas mmugent am yizerman anda ur lint ara iṭarren, ma d tizermemmuyin timeqqṛanin d tid yettemcabin ɣer yiɣucaf ama deg talɣa neɣ deg ubleɣ, akken i lant aṭas n tarrayin n tikli d westan ɣef yimanImusnawen ukzen-d ugar n 3750 n telmas n tzermemmuyin, gar-asent ugar n 500 n telmas ttidirent g Ustṛalya kan == Aglam == Tizermdmmuyin ttumeggzent d iɣersiwen inaɣlalen, tifekkiwin-nsent ttwaddlent s weglim ikenker isem-is tikbert s ddaw n tekbert-nni yella weglim aleggaɣ Ssinifent ideggan yekkawen anda tella tfukt acku tazermemmuyt ur tettili ara turmidt alamma tezɣeld tfekka-s, dɣa mi ara ad tader tseddart n wezɣal w ad tismiṭ tfekka-ynes tkeččem deg unnegzi d tarurmidt adɣa deg tegrest anda ur tzemmer ara uma ad tečč Deg yixef n tzermemmuyin llant snat n tenzarin.

Timseɣẓaẓ, d tarebbut n iɣersiwen imsiffaten yeṭṭafaren astirf n temzikrin, d tarebbut-a yakk ilan aṭas n iɣersiwen deg tfesna n temsiffatin s wazal yugaren 40% n wuṭṭun n telmas yellan deg wesmil n temseffatin
Ayaziṭ n tẓegwa awṛaɣ d talmest n uyaziṭ n tẓegwa yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tyuẓat, Yettidir deg wenẓul usamar n Asya, ini-ynes d awṛaɣ imal ar uzeggaɣ
Adeɣmus d tawsit n iɣersiwen meẓẓeyen d akernunnay d imsennen yeṭṭafar tawacult temsennin n uglim deg tfesna tesnimawin, Tla aṭas n yiniten seg uzegza ar aras d uberkan

Alefsiw d tagrawt n iweqqasen deg tewsit n ilefsiwen, Tafekka n ukefsiw-a d tufrict yettidir deg yijdi n wadda waman, Talmest-a tettwasismel d talmest yettwaggzen s umihi n wengar ɣer Tiddukla tagreɣlant i taggaẓt n tgama
Ameddul d tagrawt n yigṭaṭ n waman ur yettferfiren ara.
Iddew neɣ ibki, d aɣersiw asuṭṭaḍ yettcabin amdan deg kra n yeglamen n tfekka-ynes akked d kra deg tegzi-ynes.

Imaklasen, d adu-twacult meẓẓiyen n temseɣẓaẓ yettemcabin iɣerdayen, aṭas seg telmas-is ttwagraden-t deg kra n tmura am tid n Uruppa d Marikan, Yettwassnen d akken ila iwsan deg imi-ynes i wakken ad yeffer deg-sen učči Adu-twacult-a llant dges wazal n 25 n telmas yeṭṭafaren 7 n tewsitin == Assiseɣ d wesru == Akin-a igburen deg twacult n timaklasin yettwassers d tid nniden yellan deg wadu-twacult n tɣeṛdayt maca tizrawin tineggura malen-t ar wakken ad akzen-t 6 n twaculin.
Tawurta d aɣersiw amseksum yeṭṭafaren adu-twacult n tserɣudt, Ɣas akken Yettemcabi i wuwdan maca mgaraden deg waṭas n iglamen acku ur llin ara d yiwet n tewsit
Asfir yettwasnen s yisem n d yiwet n telmet n ugummu id yettemɣayen deg tallit n umawan
Aḍɣaɣ yettwasnen s yisem n.
Anaraf d tawsit n Imɣi seg twacult n Caprifoliaceae.
Arereǧ d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Asparagaceae.
Amezzir d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Lamiaceae.
Agurim neɣ Butenzarin d talmest n imɣan yeṭṭafaren tawsit n tazzurt, Dɣa tawsit-a d tin yeṭṭafaren twacult n temcenfar == Aglam == Agurim iga d imɣi asaɣur amazray.

Azdal d aɣersiw yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tserɣuda yettidiren deg Tefrikt dɣa yettili-d s waṭas i uwdan d umcic uwṛiɣ == Aglam == Tiddi n uzdal d tin yettiwṭen ar 85 cm s tmerniwt n 40 cm i wsallaf-is ma d addud-is ar tuyat yettawaṭ ar ugar n 50 cm, Azuk-is yettili gar n 9 kg ar 20 kg, Tafekka n uzdal d tusdidt iṭarren-is d ummiden, asallaf-is meẓẓiy Azdal yettidir gar n 12 ar 20 n iseggasen == Tudert == Azdal yettidir deg izaɣaren anda tella tuga s tuget akken i yesri iɣbula n waman ɣef wanect-a ur yettidir ara deg tneẓrufin neɣ izaɣaren ikkawen Amdan n wezdal d win iddersen s waṭas ɣef tmentilt n ugmar-is s ufus n ifganen maca ila asaduf n taggaẓt deg tmura anda yettidir, yettwasismel s ɣur Amsisi agreɣlan i tegdelt n tnezzut s telmas yettwaggzen d akken-it d talmest ur nettwaggez s umihi n wengar Tura.
Aburɣas, d asmil n iɣersiwen arimtegzaten yeṭṭafaren astirf n teswermin, Dɣa iburɣas yakk i d asismel yellan s waṭas deg ustirf n teswermin.
Tektuniyya d talmest n yemɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tanejjikt deg tfesna n tnejjikin, Tektuniyya d agummu id yettemɣayen deg tegrest yettili-d neɣ yudes ar udeffu d ifires
Amcic n tagant d aɣersiw amseksum yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tserɣuda, aɣersiw-a yettusismel deg tserɣuda timeẓyanin maca d netta yakk i d ameqran deg tewsit n yimcac
Sibbus neɣ Bufsiw d tawsit n yijqiwen yeṭṭafaren tawacult n ibufsiwen.
Siwriɣ neɣ Afsiw neɣ Bucennis d talmest n yijqiwen yeṭṭafaren tawsit n usifliw.

Asaflaw neɣ Bu tqerruyt taberkant neɣ Aberkan uqerry d talmest n yigṭaṭ yeṭṭafaren tawsit n tberdeffelt yettekkin deg twacult n tberdeffilt, Talmest-a tga d timinegt tamurant, Deg tegrest tettidir deg Tefriqt tasbegsant maca ula deg Tefriqt ugafa d Uruppa daɣen == Aglam == Awtem n usaflaw ila tebrek sufel n uqerru-yis, ma d tawtemt aqerru-yis d ačinay imal ar tezweɣ, Teɣzi n wafrawen-is mi ara ldin tettili gar n 20 ar 23 cm.
Isiɣid d yiwen n ugummu yeṭṭafaren tawsit tisiɣidt.
Tadɣaɣat d yiwen n uɣersiw yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tedɣaɣatin deg tfesna n temsuksumin, dɣa tawsit-a dges azal n 18 n telmas.
Tisfuccatin d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Aspleniaceae.

Timsennent neɣ Timerqemt d talmest meẓẓiyen n yigṭaṭ yeṭṭafaren twacult n tbenferriwin, Yettidir seg Uruppa n umalu ar Sibirya u seg Tafriqt n ugafa ar Asya talemmast yerna yettusekcem ar waṭas n yidgan deg tegnit am Ustralya d tmura n Temrikt n Wenẓul, Tettusismel deg Tiddukla tagreɣlant i taggaẓt n tgama d akken-it d talmest ur tettwaggez.
Acebcal d tawacult n temsuṭaṭ yellan deg ufelfesna n Ticebcalin yeṭṭafaren tafesna n temseɣẓaẓ deg wesmil n temsiffatin
Iẓiwec n wexxam d talmest n yigṭaṭ yeṭṭafaren tawsit n yiẓiwec.

Abuferriw neɣ Tawacult n ibuferriwen d tawacult n yigṭaṭ yettidiren deg umadal amzikan d Marikan n Ugafa, Abuferriw d afrux meẓẓiyen, ableɣ-is yettili gar n 10 cm ar 22 cm, Aṭas seg telmas n twacult-a ttidiren zdat n yimdanen anda ttafen učči-nsen am yifsan.

Ameklas uṛɣan d talmest meẓẓiyen n temseɣẓaẓ yettidiren deg Tmurt n Surya d Turkya, dɣa iga d amaklas yettwaẓunin s tuget deg yal ideg deg umadal acku kra n izeɣren n umaklas uṛɣan Gant d tilmas timegrudin

Tawurta tazeggaɣt d aɣersiw asuṭeṭ yeṭṭafaren tawsit n twurta deg twacult n tserɣuda yettidiren deg Marikan n ugafa, timesɣaz-is sskanayen-t-d d akken yella yettidir dina seg wazal n 1,8 n imelyan n iseggasen

Tarselt neɣ Tasselt imɣi yeṭṭafaren tawsit n Terselt deg tawacult n treslant yellan deg tafesna n tireslin, Tarselt d aseklu meqqren yettidiren aṭas n iseggasen, sxedmen-t igrikiyen d irumaniyen i tmugri n tinsafarin n usuji, Dɣa yettemɣayed deg tamiwin yezzin i yilel agrakal

Taninna d yiwet n telmest n iseflayen tettidir deg yakk imenẓawen n tegnit anagar Antraktika, Dɣa taninna tamezdayt d tin yettidiren deg yakk Uruppa d Tefriqt d Asya ma d talmest n iden tettidir deg yidgan yezzin i yilel agrakal akk d taninna n Mrikan yettidiren deg Marikan d Kanada
Taninna tamezdayt d talmest n iseflayen yettidiren s waṭas deg Uruppa d Asya d Tefrikt n ugafa, Aylal-a d win ilan aṭas n yiniten meẓẓiy ɣef useflay, yettafeg s tazla
Tasekkurt d assaɣ imezdi id yemmalen kra n telmas n iylalen iy lan tiseknin timarwaswasin yakk yemmudsen igan d tagemrawt, Tisekrin d tiyuzaṭ s tiddi meẓẓiyen.
Amenferriw awraɣ neɣ Turiɣt d yiwet n telmest n igṭaṭ igan d iminig s talɣa tamurant.

Vikunya neɣ Tavikunt, d tawsit n iɣersiwen imsuṭad yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tleɣmatin deg tfesna n tsenfednin ttidiren-t deg Tamrikt n Wenẓul
Abṛik d tawacult n iylalen yeṭṭafaren tafesna n twezziwin deg wadu-smil n iylalen itraren
Tizizwa n tamment d tawsit n tzizwa tettwassen n ufares d tuffra n tamment d usnulfu d tiski n teɣrasin seg wadus
Aweṭṭuf neɣ Ageṭṭuf, d tawacult n ibureɣsen timettiyin yeṭṭafaren afelwacul n tweṭṭfawin deg tfesna n tedlafriwin.

Arẓaẓ d irem id yesskanayen yal aburɣas yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tadlafriwin d wadu-tfesna n tnammasin, Druɣ yal awred aberɣas ila yiwet n telmest n irẓaẓen ma drus gemmren-t neɣ tt-jenṭiden-t fell-as ayen yettaǧǧan irẓaẓen lan azal meqqren deg usenɣed agaman deg iwerden nni

Ikayaten d tawacult n ijqiwen dges 17 n tewsitin d ugar n 167 n telmas

Tiddi tagraklant d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n Cupressaceae.
Asennan n weɣyul neɣ isri neɣ Tadart wuccen d talmest n yemɣi yeṭṭafaren tawsit n yisri deg twacult n tetrawt.
Udid d talmest n tmesdurifsan tiwamanin
Tazdayt d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n urecaceae.
Tasekla tamezdayt d aylal asekliw yettidiren deg yidgan ildin d isekla ur neflal ara s waṭas, Tasekla tamezdayt d inebgi d amezray yettgaǧǧi-d ar Tmurt n Iqbayliyen deg tegrest

Arraɣ neɣ Abareɣ azeggaɣ d yiwet n telmest n iburaɣ yeṭṭafaren tafesna n temseksumin tettwassen s umata s yisem n ubareɣ Arraɣ d aɣersiw amseksum yenfufden s waṭas yakk deg umadal acku yettili deg Alaska d Kanada d umur ameqran n Iwunak Yeddukklen n Temrikt ar Miksik d Turuft d Tefrikt n ugafa d wazal ameqran n Asya akken daɣen id t-issekcem ufgan ar Ustṛalya deg tsut tis 19, Aṭas seg iɣersiwen-a ttwagerden i lmend n weglim-nsen yettusxedmen deg tmugri n ikebbuṭen == Aglam == Arraɣ iga d talmest tameqrant yekk gar telmas n iburaɣ yeṭṭafaren tawsit n tburaɣ anda an amawaṭ yezmer wazuk-is ad yiweṭ seg 2,7 ar 6,8 kg maca azuk yemgarad seg temnaṭ ar tayedt acku irraɣen n Kanada d Alaska ttilin ugar n wid n Marikan d Uruppa d Tefrikt n ugafa, S umata iwetmen ugaren tiwetmin s wazal n 15% deg wazuk Ini n warraɣ s umata yettili d azeggaɣ deg tfekka-ynes tafellayt.

Tareddi d talmest n temseksumin yeṭṭafaren tawsit yettidir deg Marikan n ugafa d Urasya d Tmurt n Iqbayliyen, Tareddi d aɣersiw yeẓlin maca iga d anegmar idegẓen s waṭas == Aglam == Tareddi d aɣersiw usdid d aleggaɣ, teɣzi n usallaf-is tugar agla n tedɣaɣat, ini n weglim-is d aras imalen ar uzeggaɣ sufell, ma d adis-is d amellal Teɣzi n uwtem tga gar n 16 ar 31 cm, ma d tawtemt s ddaw n wannect-a Azuk n uwtem n treddi iga gar n 130 ar 450 g.
Inijjel d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Tanejjikt.
Aceffaṛ neɣ Acfiṛ neɣ Acfil neɣ Ucfiṛ neɣ Ayekfil d yiwet n tawsit n yimɣan imazrayen yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tzikemt Aṭas n telmas yeṭṭafaren tawsit-a tt-waglament ya.
Ayerni n wuccen neɣ Abeqquq n wuccen Ayerni n wuccen d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n waraceae.

Amaynag, d aɣersiw amsuṭad yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tleɣmatin deg tfesna n tsenfednin == Idgan d tmura anda yettidir == Amaynag d aɣersiw yettidiren deg yidgan isemmṭen am Mangulya d Sibirya, d tamiwin n iden deg Asya talemmast am Kazaxistan, Azerbijan, Turkmanistan, Tajakistan, Uzbakistan d Lhend == Aglam == Yettwassen umaynag d akken-it ila sin n imeddisen s umgarad n ulɣem ilan yiwen n umeddis kan, Dɣa ameddis-a d win id t-yettallen i wakken ad ifferr učči d tassemt i wakuden n usemmiṭ d tdersi, Aglim-is yeččur d azaf yettarran fell-as fell-as asemmiṭ, addud-is seg tegnit ɣer uqerru yettaweṭ ar 3 m ma d tuyat-is ar 2 m, deg wazuk yettawaṭ ar 700 kg, iṭarren-is hraw-it, ini-ynes yedda ar waras, Yettidir deg tegrawin dgi llan gar 6 ar 20 n yegmanen yesseddaw uwtem ameqran.
Tadast d tawacult n yibureɣsen yeṭṭafaten tafesna n tasenfriwin, Dɣa d tiwetmin n tafast iy tsummun idammen n wemdan akken i tga d yiwen seg ibureɣsen inesnasen yellan s tuget yakk deg umadal.
Tasnefriwin d asmil n ibureɣsen yeṭṭafaren adur n teswermin.

Ifaylellisen d tagrawt meqqren n ibureɣsen yudsen ɣer yiferṭeṭṭa, akken i gan gar n yimuddiren yellan yakk s tuget deg umadal, anda i ttidiren deg twennaṭin d yinezwa yemgaraden ula ma deg Wanda yettili wedfel d wegris.
Asennur d yiwen n uslem yeṭṭafaren tafesna n izerman yettidiren deg waman ttidirent deg waman n yilel yudsen ar teftisin n Turuft d Tefrikt d Tamrikt n ugafa
Aylal neɣ Agṭiṭ d aɣersiw ittafgen deg igenni s ifariwen.
Amermur d talmest n yimɣan imseggasen yeṭṭafar tawsit n urɣilem deg twacult n tmermurin
Aḥbac n wezrem d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Fabaceae.
Ursu amellal neɣ Ursu asafaylu, d talmest n ursunen yeṭṭafaren asmil n temsutad seg twacult n iɣelɣalen, Yettidir deg tamiwin tigersanin id yezzin ɣef Ugaraw Arktan.
Ibiw n wuccen d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n Fabaceae.
Aklil d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Lamiaceae.
Taferfra d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n wacanthaceae.

Agwanak neɣ Agwanaku d aɣersiw azagir igan d irzi seg llama yeṭṭafar tawacult n tleɣmatin, Yettemcabi s waṭas ar llama maca amgarad gar-asen d akken llama d aɣersiw amegrud ma d Agwanaku d aɣersiw azagir == Aglam == Addud n ugwanak d win yettilin gar n 1,07 d 1,25 m.
Idernen aẓidan d talmest n isekla n udernen yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tazzant.

Llama d aɣersiw asuṭṭad yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tleɣmatin yettidir deg idurar n Andiz deg Tamrikt n Wenẓul deg tmura n Ikwaduṛ, Piru, Bulivya, Čili d ugafa n umalu n Arjentin == Aglam == Addud n llama aglawan yettawaṭ gar n 109 ar 119 cm, d 120 ar 125 cm ɣer yixef, azuk-is iga gar n 130 ar 155 kg.
Agawer d talmest n ufunas yettidiren deg aneẓul n usamar n Asya, Talmest-a tettujerred d akken-it d talmest yettwaggzen s wengar deg Umuɣ azeggaɣ n IUCN seg 1986

Udad d yiwen n telmest n ifunasen yeṭṭafaren adu-twacult n tiɣeṭṭen, Yettidir deg idurar ineẓrafen n Tefriqt ugafa, Tiddi-ynes d amnummsan ur yugar ara 1,70 cm ma d azuk-is gar n 40 ar 145 kg i wewtem amawaṭ.

Tizikmarin d tafesna n ibureɣsen war afriwen, igmamen n tafesna ayi ur ttwamhazen ara s waṭas seg mi i d-uflalen deg tallit tadivunayt yakk d tissisin == Aglam == Igmamen n tegrawt-a d wid yettidiren s talɣa tagejdant ɣef tmadɣaɣin d iseffaluyen d yiẓra akken i tetten tafurri d wadal.

Ameddurdu d aɣersiw amseksum yettidiren deg ugafa n Turuft Akked Asya d Marikan, Ameddurdu d netta yak i d aɣersiw ameqran deg twacult n tedɣaɣatin, dɣa netta d aɣerdiw yuddsen tafekka-ynes teččur d aksum, Učči ynes yezzi ɣef ikesman imi netta yettekkin deg tfesna n temseksumin.
Agenduz d mmis n tfunas yettuɣ alen d Tafunast neɣ d Azger Mara ad yimɣur deg addar

Uddis akruran d tanga takrurant id yennulfan seg sin iferdisen neɣ ugar s wazal armeskil ad yesbded-n tameddast-is, Amdya: aman d uddis yesɛan Uksijin d Hidṛujin s wazal n 1:2, S umata azal-a Yessefk ad yeqqim d armeskil i kra n ibelkimen isengamen mači i yikayaden ifganen, ɣef aya kra n iyufa am udaruɣ yettwaḥseb d ageṭṭum mači d uddis.
Azzeng, Azamul akruran Zn n iferdisen n tezrart tamezwart deg isinen n tukkit annect-a ɣef tilin n tuzziyin d tilmawin deg tuzzya d
Aman (H2O) d tanga yellan deg wakal.

Amitan d uddis akruran igan d afraran deg Tehidṛukaṛbunin, U Netta d agaz ilan taftart takrurant CH4, Mitan azedgan ur ili ara tikdi, Maca mara ad yettusexdem deg uzenzu yettwarway d tifrit ilan tikida
Iɣir neɣ Anas d aferdis akruran ig keččemen deg tigri n igeṭman dgi yettunernu i wureɣ i wakken ad s-ternu taɣuṛi, Akken daɣen yettwamugri yyis yedrimen
Tanicca d azṛu abliɣan ansilicun yeqquren s waṭas tettwasileɣ-d seg wuguggi asengam akken i yettwabna s usaɣir zeddigen.
Ageṭṭum d tiddukla gar n sin iferdisen ikruraren neɣ ugar, Maca yessefk deg yiwen deg-sen ad yili d asin, igeṭman ttilin lan iylan d isineyyen
Alkan deg tekrura tagmant d uddis uhidṛukaṛbun yettusṛwan,Qqnen dges ibelkimen n ukaṛbun yal yiwet ar tayedṭ
Hidṛujin d aferdis akruran azamul-is H Uṭṭun-is abelkim 1, Yezga-d deg tuzya tamezwart n iferdisen s-ufell n iferdisen n tegrawt tamezwart

Aɣuzzer neɣ Azallu neɣ Ahallun d aferdis akruran azamul-is Sn, uṭṭun-is abelkim 50 deg uyiren imezzi, Yettili deg ugama s waddad aquran, Deg tama takrurant yerwes ar sin iferdisen it-yudsen : Aldun d ujirmanium

Aldun d aferdis akruran Azamul-is PB ma d uṭṭun-is abelkim 82, Yella deg uyiren awalan deg tegrawt n ukarbun, Aldun d amɣuz aẓayan s tneẓẓawt iflalen deg waddaden igamanen yettili s yini aẓerfan yezzegzun
Ihiǧǧ neɣ Azerniɣ d aferdis akruran azamul-isAsma d uṭṭun-is abelkam 33 deg uyiren imezzi n iferdisen, Takura-ynes tabelkamt 74.922.
Akaṛbun d aferdis akruran azamul-is C Uṭṭun-is abelkim 6 Yezga-d deg tuzya tis 2 n iferdisen ɣef yixef n tegrawt tis 14 deg uyiren imezzi
Tifrit neɣ Tizefrit d aferdis akruran arasin, Azamul-is akruran S, Ma d uṭṭun -is abelkim 16, Yettusexdem deg tmugri n ugari d tṭerqacin

Izeffaren ikaṛbuksilinen d izeffaren igmanen yellan deg usismel n tegrawt n ukaṛbuksil tamesɣant, Yettak-d i weprutun taftart-is tamatant R-, d asemselsay ya d aẓaṛ alkylan neɣ d abelkim n uhidṛujin, Dɣa yettili s waṭas deg ugama.
Alkul d awal yettwasxedmen deg tkimit tagemnawt i yakk uddisen ikimanen dgi tella tegrawt tawurant tahidṛuksilt s tezrart tahidrukarbunt
Asin deg takrura d aferdis akruran izellin tiliktrunin i wakken ad yeg t-ion-in tilawin akken daɣentella turza tasinayt gar n ibelkimen-is
Aferdis akruran d tanga takrurant dgi ur yettwazmer ara usegzem d usezgen-is tesɛa yiwen n ubelkim akken daɣen id ittnumuẓ Uṭṭun abelkim
Adus d tanga tasemmayt yeqquren tettusexdem i wagaẓ n tɣawsiwin yemgaraden d tmugri n tsiɣin
Azeffar d yal uddis akruran yezmer mara ad yefsi deg waman ad yeslelli Tipṛutunin n uhidṛujin
Alkin deg tekrura tagmant d ahidṛukaṛbun ur nettwaseṛwu, Dges ma drus yiwet n turza timisint gar n sin n ibelkimen n ukaṛbun.
Tayla n uzemmur d afares n weẓmay n taqqayin n uzemmur id tettak tzemmurt, afares n uzemmur yettili-d aladɣa di tmura yejban i yil agrakal
Tanga di Tasengama d ayen yakk yesɛan azuk, Tanga tesɛa aṭṭas n inumaẓ am: afendir, Ableɣ, Tiddi.
Tignewt titriklant d tissi n igazen id yezzin f jra n tfekka tayafuyt ilan tasmekta issefken i teldayt sgi id ijebbed tiɣawsiwin-a
Taggult neɣ Adaryes d talmest n yimɣan yeṭṭafaren tawsit n wuffal deg twacult n tbiwin.
Aḍad d aḥric seg ufus n wemdan neɣ n kra n yiɣersiwen, yezga-d ɣer yixef n ufus.
isirew d agman id nettaf deg wezgen ameqran n temseffatin, isirew yettili-d d sin n izegnan, ad naf yiwen n usirew deg kra n imuddiren am ufgan d tifunasin neɣ ayis, Akken llan imuddiren iden ilan
Aglim d agman iy teddlen tafekka talsant d tfekkiwin n waṭas n iɣersiwen niden.
Tisiqqest d agman asetnaw yettuqnen tikwal s ifexsi ariran deg kra n iɣersiwen d iburɣas

Ifeɣmes neɣ Tiggaz d talmest gar telmas n tuɣmas i yellan deg uɣesmaṛ n ifganen d temsuṭaṭ s umata, yella ar zdat n uɣusmar Afellay d wadday == Tawuri == Ɣer waṭas n timestuga yakk d irammaten am ufgan ifeɣmasen gan d tuɣmas yessezgan i wegzam n wučči, maca ɣer temcac d uglan iy gezzemen aksum d wučči acku ifeɣmasen-is meẓẓey-it == Amdan == Amdan n ifeɣmasen d win yemgaraden s unect n telmest d twacult n uɣersiw, amdya ar ufgan llan 8 n ifeɣmasen ma ɣer temsuṭaṭ iden am yimcac d iysan llan 12, ɣer temseɣẓaẓ 4.
Tafekka talsit neɣ ljetta n bnadem.
Allaɣ d azgen ameqran yakk deg anagraw anesur alemmas,
icc d timerna tinegzanin n yeɣsan id yettemɣayen deg uqerru n izerzer
Tazamart d azrug neɣ d abrid n wezwu agejdan yebṭan ar izrugen isnawanen yessawaṭen azwu ar turin.
Turin neɣ Aberfiw d agman agejdan deg unagraw amesgunef n wemdan d waṭas n iɣersiwen niden gar-asen ula kra n telmas n iselman d kra n iɣlalen.
Adeffu d yiwen gar n telmas n imɣan
Tissirt d tuɣmest id yezgan seg tama tamendeffirt n uɣesmaṛ yettwasxedm deg tuẓda n wučči sɣur ufgan d kra n telmas n iɣersiwen neɣ timsuṭad

Tuɣmas tuɣmest d agman yeqquren am yiɣess dges iẓuran yeddan s agensu n uɣesmar n wadda d win n ufella n tewsit n timtegzitin = Tawuri n tuɣmas = = Tilmas n tuɣmas = Llan-t 4 n telmas n tuɣmas: Ifeɣmes neɣ Tinegzamin: D tuɣmas id yezgan zdat n uɣesmar n ufella d win wadda, Llan-t dges 8 n tuɣmas Tawuri-ynes d agzan d ucerreg n wučči Uglan: D tuɣmas imesden talɣa-nsent temmug am ukeṛdasLlan-t 4 n wuglan, Yal snat zdat n ifeɣmes Tawuri-ynes d acerreg n wučči, Nezmer ad n-ini tettalel ifeɣmes deg aya Tissirin:Llan-t 12 n tsirrin.
Iccer d tanga taqurant iy teddlen ixfawen n yiṭudan n ifassen d tfednin n yiṭarren n wemdan d waṭas n telmas n iɣersiwen.
Icc deg tesnudert d tariẓt deg weglim id itteffɣen seg uqerru n waṭas n telmas n iɣersiwen am izerzer d tfunasin
Ugel d tuɣmas imesden id yezgan gar n tissirt d ifeɣmes
Ajeǧǧig neɣ Taslawit d agman agensas ɣef temhalt n umyaraw n tmesdurifsanin.
iɣess d agmam d aquran id itgin amur deg taɣessa Deg tfekka n ufgan llan-t ugar n 270 n teɣsatin, Mi ara ad yemɣur ufgan ttenṭaṭent neɣ ddukulen-t kra deg-sent alama uɣalen-t deg 206 n teɣsatin.
Ṛṛus d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n brassicaceae.
Afus ɣer ufgan d agman gar yegmanen ifellayen, yezga-d deg taggara n yiɣil.
Takwat neɣ Tabniqt d tigget tamesniyt d twurayt deg imuddiren, Acku yal amuddir yettwasni seg yiwet n tebniqt neɣ ugar, ttufarsen-t tebniqin seg unegzum abenniq seld n gemmu-ynes
Agiger d tama yellan di tlemmast n tfekka n ufgan, yettezruzzuɣ-d deg-s yiri d yirawen iminag d yirawen imazdaren.
Abbaɣ d iɣes n uqerru.
D aḥric n tfekka n wemdan akk d iɣersiwen

Tuɣmest n ugerru' d Tuɣmest tameggarut id igemmun deg taggara n uɣesmaṛ dɣa Azgen ameqran n ifganen lan 4 n tuɣmas n ugerru, Tuɣmest n ugerru tgemmud deg tallit n waddar yettilin gar n 18 ar 25 iseggasen
Ammas d amur-nni deg wadis yellan gar n isekni ademraw d taɣma.
Tiṭ d aẓeṭṭa ubrin i d-yezgan seddaw n timmi d unyir, Akdu n ufgan amawaṭ yettawaṭ ar 2,5 cm, Tiṭ tla 6 n tmaẓwalin i d-iten-teswliwlen.
iri neɣ amegreṭ d agman yessawaṭen aqerruy s igiger deg imuddiren n inaɣlalen
Idmaren d amur seg usemmili n ufgan yakk d usemmili n iɣersiwen niden, yezga-d gar n tuyat d wadis.

Anagraw anesur alemmas d Azgen ameqran yakk n unagraw anesur amatam, Tiddukla-ynes d anagraw anesur afulman d unagraw anesur afekkan yesskanay-d ayen umi neqqar Anagraw anesur ilan tiremt d wazal ameqqran deg tikeli n iɣersiwen s umata d ifganen aladɣa
Asallaf neɣ Adfar d agman yettilin deg tmeccact neɣ taggara n tfekka n uɣersiw am temsuṭad d tɣirdmiwin d temraradin
Tamart d tama taddayt n udem s ddaw n ucenfir, Dges id yettemɣay ucamar

Anagraw anesur d anagraw anamaẓ yakk deg tgelda n uɣersiw, Yella yakk deg imuddiren seg tmenza ar timesiffatin, Yettili d tagrawt n tmezziyin tifrarin n teskikin deg tmenza skud nettali deg yisili n temhazt trennu tseddart n tkerrust-is aladɣa deg ufgan
Ajgu n uzagur neɣ Ajgu n warur ɣer imuddiren imtegzaten d tagrawt n teɣlalin yulmen i taggaẓt n uleqqin iy teddun s teɣzi-ynes.
Taglimt n uqerru d agman id yezgan sufell d gar n wudem d yiri
Anagraw amesgunef neɣ Allal amesgunef d agman n afekkan id yettajjun Uksijin imsefki n wermud n tfekka n ufgan akken ig tekkes fellas anaksid n ukaṛbun ..
Tirɣudin neɣ Tisdaṛ Tinefra d agman uwnis inṭṭen yakk d umgun s tmiṭṭ deg usirew, itteffeɣ-d seg usirew n tyemmat deg taɣser tis 3 n tarrawt
Asasfay akruran d tanga takrurant yettwarnun ar uferdis i wselfu n tsedmirt takrurant neɣ i wkayad war tasedmirt,

Acubar deg takrura d tigget tameẓyant yakk n tenga takrurant, Yettarey tasuddest-is takrurant d iylan-is, Tiɣri n ucabur d tussna-ynes d ayla n tekrura, Akken daɣen tella tezrawt iylan n ucabur s tsengama isem-is tasengama tacubrayt
Alkyl d aẓaṛ amyiwen n tugdut yesɛan abelkim n ukaṛbun d uhidṛujin yettwasnin deg telɣa n tezrart, Talkylin tgint-d tazrart tasnulut, Yerna tesɛa tagda CnH2n+1

Anyat neɣ inyaten n iferdisen ikruraren d talɣiwin n iferdisen ikruraren, abelkim-is yesɛa yiwen n uṭṭun abelkim, Maca Kan temgarad deg tkura tabelkamt af tmentilt n wemgarad deg uṭṭun n tnyutrunin, Iylan ikruraren ur ttemgaraden ara d ubelkim yakk d unyat-is

Taswast tanayyurt d taswast i d-immalen azemz s unect n talɣa n wayyur, anda deg tuget n tegnatin d wakuden ayyur yessemtay ɣef tmeẓriwt tamaynut n wayyur amedya deg teswast tineslemt, taswast tehibṛut, taswast tacenwit d taswast tahendit yeggunin yakk ɣef tuzzya n wayyur

Taswast neɣ Tafada d allal n usiden n wakud i wsiden n yizmaz d wussan d usuddes-nsen i yimesɣuṛa imettiyen, imesɣanen, ideblanen yakk d imsenziyen, anecta yettili-d s isebdaden yemgaraden deg teswasin yemgaraden, deg yakk taswasin-nni ttunefken kra n yismawen i kra n talliyin n uzemz anda tikwal ttilin d ussan neɣ d imalas neɣ d ayyuren neɣ d iseggasen, dɣa deg waṭas n tikkal ttilin d ayyuren yakk d iseggasen i teddun yakk d tuzzya n tfukt deg igenni yakk d wansa n tegnit deg tmezzit-is ɣef tfukt, neɣ teddun yakk d tlallit d taggara n wayyur akken daɣen illant teswasin yettganin ɣef tuzya n wayyur d tfukt d isin.
Taswast tineslemt d taswast tanayyurt yeggunin ɣef tuzzya n wayyur i tukza n wayyuren.
Tanfalit taswast Taṛumant temmal-d s umata tiswasin i sseqdacen Iṛumanen almi d asmi i d-tennulfa teswast tajulyant deg 45 send talalit n Ɛisa.

Tuččit d afray id yesskanayen turit s wekmaz maca ur yettwasismel ara d talmest seg yifrayen, Acku tasnujjya tatrart tessken-d d akken tuččit d tin imalen neɣ yettemcabin ar takma, Anda isalan ttasen-asen-d sɣur inzizen inessuren iwer imyiliyen yellan deg weglim yakk yettili-d usiweṭ n isalan s talɣa tulmist sɣur sin n inagrawen igejdanen igan d Adis n usensul yakk d tkemmust n inessuren.
Asekkud d yiwet gar 5 tinliwin dgi tiṭṭ d wallaɣ zemren ad snirmen tayyugin tizaradikranin n tafat i wssegzu n wayen yettwaẓren
Arwas neɣ Taẓimdalt d tasakrart yettenfufuden gar n yimdanen s tazzla meqqren deg tjumma meqqren am umenẓaw akken iy zmer ad yemken ad yenfufed ar umadal yakk.

Adrar n Ṭariq (s tanglizit: Gibraltar), d tahrest (colonie) tabriṭanit tamecṭuḥt, tezga-z deg wenẓul (sud) n Spenyul, ɣef Yilel Agrakal.
Tiɣilt d taddart deg tɣiwant n Cemmini

Idurar n Himalaya d azrar n idurar yellan deg umenẓawa n Asya teẓẓun izaɣaren n uzunmenẓaw n Lhend af agni n Tibit, Dges azal n 9 n tqacucin yeflalen yakk deg tegnit maca tameqqrant akk deg-sent d adrar n Everest s wazal n 8,848 m deg teflel.
Azrar n idurar neɣ Tiraf neɣ Tizunt neɣ Tazrar d ademkal yeqqnen aṭas n yidurar deg yiwen n wedras
igenni d imeẓri id yettbinen seg tagnit ar tallunt

Idurar n Ṛuki d azrar n idurar id yezgan deg utaram n umenẓaw n Marikan n ugafa yumẓen ɣef tjumma n 4,8000 km² seg tamiwin tigafayin n ugezdu n Britc kulumbya n kanada ar agezdu n Meksiku tamaynut deg wenẓul utrim n Marikan, Taqacuct n albirt teflal nnig n 4,399 m.
Asnay d agi n tɣawsa deg yideg amazgay

Tusnakt d tussna yimḍanen s umata, tettwa sileɣ s tmusniwin timadwanin (connaissances abstraites) s tallat n izebzan imeẓlan (raisonnements logiques) ɣef tmiḍranin (concepts) am yimḍanen (nombres), tanezgit (géométrie), tiskiwin (structures) neɣ iseɣwal (transformation).
Tusnazduɣt neɣ Tareygama d yiwen n ufurek n tesnudert yeɣɣaren tisedmirin gar n yimuddiren d twennaṭ-is tasnegmudrant igebren seg yimuddiren d isegra ur neddir ara.
Tasensileɣt deg tesnudert d tussna yeɣɣaren talɣa d tiski n imuddiren yakk d iglamen-is yakk d talɣa d tiski n imuren n ugensu am yiɣsan d igmanen
Tasnaɣersiwt d tarrayt tusnant yeɣɣaren ɣef iɣersiwen, Tasnaɣersiwt d angaz seg tasnudert dgi tella daɣen tɣuri n yemɣan umi qqaren tasnimɣan
Aselkim d tamacint taliktṛunant n usiḍen.
Asemmili d yiwen n ufurk n tesnudert izerrew talɣa d tmuski n imuddiren yakk d yimuren-nsen.
Tameẓla anamek ines: tussna d tigzi talsant.

Tasnallunt d tussna n wanay n wayen akk itezzin neɣ yettilin deg tallunt neɣ ayen yeffɣen yakk i tignewt titriklant n tegnit, ama d itran d imtiwgen, d iseffuden, neɣ d ismilen Tasnallunt d tussna tamzikt s waṭas i d-yennulfan si tallit n teglest, mi bdan imesnallunen imezwura ttmuqulen s webrid azrawan s igenni, dɣa gzan deg-s aṭas n tlufa i ten-iɛawnen ula deg tudert n yal ass am yinig deg de yillel, maca tezga texleḍ d wayen iwumi qqaren aneǧǧem i icudden ugar ɣer ukerrer.

Tafizikt taɣisant d yiwen n umur seg tfizikt izerrwen aɣyay abelkam deg wayen yezzin ɣef tzelɣa taferdisant deg weɣyay igebren seg yipṛutunen d yinyutrunen, ttwaqqanen u ttemyermaden gugar-asen mi ara ad yili usummu n tzelɣiwin tiferdisanin seg beṛṛa.
Tussna n wayen yettikin di tanga d wamek tettbeddil.
Takimit tagmant d yiwen n wengaz n tkimit, iylan d tsedmirt n uddisen akk d tengiwin tigmanin akken daɣen id tefka azal i tsedmirin ikecmen deg temsuka n imuddiren neɣ id itt-ffɣen deg-sent
Tasegda d taẓuri meqqren
Aljiber neɣ Aljiber d amur ger imuren n tusnakt ig zerwen s tugett tiskiwin tiljibriyin (structures algébriques), am tefekka deg Aljiber (corps en algèbre).

Tasnitit deg tfelsaft d yiwen n ingazen ilan azal meqren deg tedfersengamt, Tusna ayi teɣɣar deg unagi deg wesnirem n ugama n tilit arangan deg tlufa tidfersengamin id yellan seg tsugnin d irman d ilugan usnanen.
Tadfersengamt d angaz deg tfelsaft yeɣɣaren tumast n tɣawsiwin am isteqsiyen n tilit d illi d tilawt, Awal n ugama dayi d win yennilin ar tgamat n tɣawsiwin d tmentilin-is d wayen umi tella
Tanzeggit d tigezmi tameqrant ger igzumen n tusnakt d win i izerwen tiwellatin neɣ Udmawen deg tallunin s myal tasekta, deg tsekta Tis krad nezmar ad nemmeslay ɣef tenzeggit tuklidt.
Awal tafelsuft yusa-d si tegrigit phylosophia φιλοσοφία philosophía yesɛan anamek “tayri n tussna” neɣ “tayri n tmussni”.
Tasengama d tussna n tanga d umussu ines, daɣen n tallunt d wukud.
Tasnafsit, d tussna ay yeqqaren ɣef wamek ay tetteddu tnefsit n wemdan ed wuguren ay izemren ad tt-aɣen.

Tinnagrawt deg tussniwin n tudert d umezruy agaman d tussna tuzdigt n usismel n temsurta deg snat n talliyin d wassaɣ gar Imuddiren deg talliyin, s tenfalit tamatant d ayen ara ad yeǧǧen amdan ad yegzu amezruy anemhaz n tudert deg tegnit Tikwal, irem n tennagrawt d win yemmegdan d yirem n usismel n tesnudert, akken ig yezmer daɣen ad yemmerwi d usismel ussnan == Ifurken d isnasen == inagmayen ssexdamen deg tezrawt n tennagrawt tasnudrant ifurken yemgaraden i wakken ad rnun ad gzun aṭas ɣef wassaɣ gar Imuddiren yemgaraden, ifurken-a ttwasxedmen i sbadu n isnasen d isexdamen n inagrawen itraren Tinnagrawin tisnudranin ssismilent tilmas s 3 n ifurken imezlayen.
Tasnudert niɣ tudrussna niɣ tussna n tudert d tussna ɣef wayen akk yettidiren.
Tusniwin tigmawin d tusniwin yeɣɣaren neɣ yeqqaren idisan tisengamatin tigamatin tiyufatin i yakk tumanin yettilin deg tegnit d tallunt
== Agzul == Tasnilest d tussna i izerwen tameslayt akked tutlayt.
Talsasnet d aḥric n tussna talsant d-yaanna d wefgan, bnadem neɣ medden ama deg amek mugen neɣ weqmen, tikli-nsen, d yidles nsen.
D taɣult gar taɣulin n tesnilest i d-yelhan d tezrawt n unamek n wawalen d wassaɣ i lan gar-asen ama deg talɣa, ama deg unamek.

Takelsertit d tussna ay yeqqaren ɣef wassaɣen gar tmura/akal ed nnfeɛ ay yellan deg-sen akked tsertit, am wakk-n ay teqqar ɣef wassaɣen gar Yiwunak ed temsizzelt gar-asen akk-n yal yiwen deg-sen ad yaweḍ ɣer nnfeɛ-nnes deg kra n tama n umaḍal.
Amerway deg takrura d arway n sin iyufa israwen neɣ ugar
Ageṭṭum d tiddukla gar n sin iferdisen ikruraren neɣ ugar, Maca yessefk deg yiwen deg-sen ad yili d asin, igeṭman ttilin lan iylan d isineyyen
Tadamsa, d anagraw n wembaddel ay d-yettilin gar yemdanen neɣ tiṛmisin deg wenrar n tnezzut.
Taɣreft d adras amessarti deg tsartut n tesnudert tezga-d sufel n udras n ifelasmil d ddaw n wesnay n wadu-twacult
Deg tesnudert, tawacult d tamsartut issegrewen tiwsitin id yekksanayen tireswin timeqranin gar-asent.
Deg tasnudert, asmil d aswir wis kraḍ n useggi amagnu n tilmas timuddirin (ẓeṛ anagrawan).
Adu-telmest deg tsensartut d aswir anemmas i d-yezgan srid s ddaw n telmest deg usismel n Linné Adu-telmest deg tsenɣersiwt tettumeggez d aswir amessarti amyiwen yellan s ddaw n telmest.

Deg tasnudert, Tafesna d aswir wis kiẓ deg tsartut n tesnudert yal tafesna n imuddiren tegzem ar waṭas n twaculin iy gezmen s iman-is ar yismilen == Tigariwin tilatiniyin i ttaken asertatu == Isem n immizewren yettfuk s udfir -ales ɣur leḥcawec, adalen dɣa igersalen.
Tawsit d Adras amessarti n unagi neɣ n unadi deg tasartut tusnant n telmas yeɣɣaren deg waɛas n imuddiren yettemcabin deg talɣa d uẓaṛ.

Talmest deg tesnudert d yiwet n tigget n usismel asnudran agejdan, Akken i tga d adras amessarti agejdan deg tsensartut, Talmest tettwassen d akken-it d tagrawt n imuddiren ig zemren ad mmreclen gugar-asen w ad farsen tarwa, Ɣas akken asenmel ayi ur d-ikeffu ara deg waṭas n waddaden maca yella wemray deg usenmel n irem n telmest, Dɣa anect-a yettwassen s wugur n talmest acku deg waṭas n wakuden ttwasxedmen wawalen n iden am tasnasileɣt d ullun areygaman
Deg anagrawan, 'astirf (neɣ phylum) d aswir wis sin n aseggi amagnu n tilmas timuddirin.
Isem-is s latinit: Nerium oleander
Imidek d tawsit n Imɣi seg twacult n Anacardiaceae.
Tiseflay neɣ Tiseflayin d tawacult n iylalen yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tiseflalɣiwin dges 60 n telmas ttekkan-t yakk deg tsekliwin == Aglam == Tiseflayin d iylalen isekliwen meẓẓiyen neɣ imnummsen.
Ccer n yilef d tawsit n yemɣi seg twacult n poaceae.
Awaquṛ d tawsit n yigṭaṭ yeṭṭafaren tawacult n iwuqaṛ.
Asemlal neɣ Ccix n lebqul, d yiwet n tewsit n yemɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tsemlalin
Angazsartu neɣ Clade d tawsit tasartawt dgi yalla yiwen n uẓar amezday ayen yakk id ittekked dges yettili d aynazɣer
Tanejjikt d tawacult tamɣawt n tesnayyawin dges aṭas n tewsitin n isekla d tmedkin azal ameqran deg-sent ttemɣayent-d deg yidgan isemmṭen
Tuɣmest n temɣart d tawsit n yemɣi seg twacult n westeraceae.

Tamsartut deg tasnudert d tiget tasuddist yesɛan aṭas n imuddiren, yal tamsartut tesɛa isem d agla-s, Akken daɣen yessefk ad tili s ddaw n yisem-is usnan dɣa ismawen-a d wid id yettwakksen ya seg tlatint neɣ seg tegrikt.
== Tilmas ==
Illan d yan imɣi iskaren yan ugummu.
Tifadin d tawacult n yimɣan.

Timseksumin d yiwet n tfesna n temsuṭaṭ ilan azal n 260 n telmas n tuthiryin, Azgen ameqran n temseksumin tettent aksum kan, lant uglan d ikacbaren d wallen i d-tittallen i wakken ad tesnirem tigemrawin.
Tiserɣuda d tawacult n iɣersiwen isuṭad dgi llan-t waṭas n telmas am yizmawen d iɣilasen d imayasen d yemcac d izem n idurar d waṭas n telmas n iden
Tazzant d tawacult n isekla imagnulanen yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tezzanin.

Tizutar d tafesna n temraradin id yekkren send n 85 n imelyan n iseggasen neɣ tallit umi qqaren Tallit tasisfayt, Nezmer ad n-ini d tizutar d tafesna yudsen ar waylalen, Deg tzutar llan wazal n 23 n telmas ur nengir ara, 14 deg sent deg tawacult n iɣucaf d Yiwet n Taligaturin ɣas akken llan-t waṭas n telmas iden inegren
Tigerfiwin d tawacult n igṭaṭ yettidiren deg yakk imenẓawen n tegnit, Dges ugar n 120 n telmas gar-asent: ajaɣiɣ, ijilem, Timesferẓatin
Tiddiwin d tawacult n yimɣan imazufsanen yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tiddiwiyin deg wesmil n taydiwiyin.
Tizermemmuyin timeskebrin d afelafesna yeṭṭafaren astirf n temzekrin, Llant snat n tfesniwin deg tzermemmuyin timeskebrin

Timeskebrin d tafesna n iɣersiwen yeṭṭafaren asmil n temraradin, Timeskebrin d nettat yakk i d tafesna dgi llan-t waṭas n telmas gar n wesmil n temraradin s wazal n 59% tiddirent deg yakk idgan n tegnit anagar Antraktika, Deg temskebrin llan-t snat n tegrawin: imiglen d tzermemmuyin
Titbirin d tawacult n iylalen dgi llan-t waṭas n tewsitin d telmas, llan-t kra n telmas yessegred wemdan yessxdem i tuzna n tebratin am itbir iminig
Isemlel d tawsit n tmedkin d yimɣan isaɣuren yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tnarafin.
Tidmamay d tawsit n Imɣi seg twacult n Asteraceae.
Mernuyet d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Lamiaceae.
Irem Olea yaɛqel tamessartut, tawsit Olea, tagrumma n leḥcawec yesɛan tiɣariwin tucrikin.
Afeqqus n weɣyul d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Cucurbitaceae.
Taneɣrazt neɣ Tiɣrazin d tawacult n yimɣan yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tmejjirin deg wesmil n tesnayyawin.
Tizzadfarin d tafesna n ibureɣsen yeṭṭafaren adu-smil n tarfriwin.
Tiburaɣ d yiwet n tewsit n taydiyyin yettidiren deg waṭas n yidgan deg umadal, Tawsit-a dges azal n 12 n telmas i yettwassnen yakk deg-sent d abareɣ azeggaɣ yakk d ubareɣ asafaylu.
Tasekla neɣ Tasedla d tawsit n yimɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult n titriyyin, Deg tewsit-a llant wazal n 120 n telmas amur ameqran deg-sent yettemɣay-d deg Uruppa d Asya d Tefrikt
Addad neɣ Akicaw d tawsit n imɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tetrit deg tfesna n tetriyyin.
Bu narjuf d tawsit n Imɣi seg twacult n Solanaceae.
Tigetlin neɣ Tawacult n tgetlin d yiwet n twacult yeṭṭafaren tafesna n iyerzizen yellan deg wesmil n temsiffatin, dges ad naff agtul akk d imerwel.
Timejjirt d tawacult tamɣawt dgi llan-t ugar n 200 n tewsitin d ugar n 2300 n telmas am tebduɣt d mejjir
igmariyen neɣ Tigmariyin d yiwen n usismel i tawacult n kra n telmas n wayisen d iɣersiwen yettaken aẓaṛ am weɣyul d imisred d telmas n iden inegren, Tigmariyin ṭṭafaren-t tafesna n tsuffenza
Lbecna d talmest n Imɣi seg twacult n Poaceae.
Timsennenin d tawsit meqqren n iylalen yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tbenferriwin
Tinejjikin d tafesna n yemɣan yeṭṭafaren asmil n tesnayyawin deg twaculin-is tella tnejjikt dgi llant waṭas n tewsitin n isekla d tmedkin id yettemɣayen aladɣa yidgan semmṭen
Arjagnu neɣ Aqlilu d tawsit n yimɣan isaɣuren yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tetrawt.
Tasnakt d tawsit n yemɣi seg twacult n hypericaceae.
Anekraf d tawsit n Imɣi seg twacult n Fabaceae.
Takaṛmust d tawsit yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tkaṛmusin deg tfesna n tinɣerflin
Ileggi d tawsit n yemɣi seg twacult n fabaceae.
Tinsnadamin d tawsit n yemɣi seg twacult n lamiaceae.
Aɣilas d yiwet gar n tewsitin n tserɣuda dgi llant 4 n telmas yettwassenen yakk
Ikfil neɣ Akfal d tawsit n yimɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tsisant s unect n usismel aklasik, neɣ tizikemt s unect n usismel amhazɣer
Tamersa, d yiwet n tewsit n yemɣan akk d izegza yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tmesferranin deg tfesna n tmessferranin dges azal n 42 n telmas yettwasentmen d waṭas n telmas ur ttwasntment ara
Timaklasin d tawacult n temseɣẓaẓ, Akin-a igburen ttwasersen d adu-twacult deg Muridae maca tizrawin tineggura malen-t ar usersi n 6 n twaculin.
== Tilmas ==
Blitu d tawsit n yemɣi seg twacult n wamaranthaceae.
Taɣeṛdayt d tawacult n iɣersiwen imsuṭad yeṭṭafaren tafesna n temseɣẓaẓ dges ugar n 1100 n telmas, Deg tewsitin-is yella iɣeṛdayen, iɣuliyen d idwiyen
Tirizwa neɣ iles ufunas d yiwet n tewsit n yemɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult Tarizwant ilan iǧeǧǧigen d izegzawen rewsen iwnayna.

Tabuda d tawsit n yimɣan iynayawwen, Tawsit-a d tin yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tbudayt,Yettwassnen ɣef telmas n tewsit-a d akken ttemɣayent-d deg yirawen neɣ idisan n Wanda llan waman am igelmimen d ibelmaten d isafen neɣ a umata deg yideggan igrawanen.
Tiyuzaṭ d tafesna n iylalen ẓẓayen deg tfekka, Tafesna ayi dges abibi, Ayaziṭ n ideflawen, Yuzaṭ, Tajirra, Tasekkurt n ideflawen, Tasekkurt d yiferd

Tibuzgrayzin d tawacult n yijqiwen igebren seg 6 n tewsitin d wazal n 70 n telmas n tbuzegrayziyin d tbisbisin d tbisbiyin == Aglam == Tibuzgrayzin d tagrawt n yigṭaṭ ilan tafekka d tusdidt, S tiddi meẓẓiyen neɣ yemnummsen, irawen-nsent meẓẓiy-it.
Tiznefriwin d tafesna n ibureɣsen yeṭṭafaren adur n teswermin.
Titrit d tawacult n imɣan yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tetrawin deg wesmil n tasnayyawin.
Taɣeddiwt d tawsit n yimɣan imezgiyen yeṭṭafaren tawacult n titrit.
Tiwetlɣatin d tafesna n iɣersiwen imsuṭad yettugezmer ar snat n twaculin: iwetlen d Tipikawin, Ttunegzent ar 13 n tewsitin d 80 n telmas, Ttemcabin-t s waṭas ar temseɣẓaẓ deg tikliwin-nsent
Thuya d talmest n yemɣi seg twacult n cupressaceae.
Wacnaf d Imɣi n twacult n Brassicaceae.
Iɣri, d tawsit n yemɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult n teɣrit dges azal n 15 n telmas.
Tizifut neɣ Taɣadyut d tawsit n yimɣan id yettemɣayen deg tamiwin yezzin i wemda n yilel agrakal yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tetrawt.
Tafuzzalt d tawsit tamɣawt yeṭṭafaren tawacult tafuzzlant deg tfesna n tmejjirin, Deg tewsit-a llan-t 55 n telmas ittwadagen d 158 n telmas urad ur ttwadagent
Talliẓin d tawacult n imɣan yeṭṭafaren asmil n tasnayyawin.

Ibeldisen d asmil meqqren yakk deg wadur n tigritin acku dges azal n 80% n telmas yeṭṭafaren adur-a, akken daɣen i tga d tafesna tameqrant tis snat yakk deg tgelda taɣersawt anda i llant dges wazal n 65000 n telmas gar-asent aɣlal d umillus d tezɣurt.
Iskerci neɣ Tanesfalt d talmest n yimɣan yeṭṭafaren tawacult n teskercin.
Tazeggart d tawsit n yemɣi seg twacult n Rhamnaceae.
Affar d tawsit n Imɣi seg twacult n Poaceae.

Tumedt d tawacult n yimɣan yeṭṭafaren tafesna n tumdin igan d tafesna n taynayyawin, Tawacult n tumdin d yiwet seg twaculin n yimɣan yeǧuǧugen tegber seg wazal n 600 n tewsitin yeẓẓunin ɣef wazal n 10,000 n telmas gar n telmas-a llan imendiyen am temẓin, Aṛuz, irden, ukbal, Aẓekkun d yinelli akken daɣen i tegber seg waṭas n isaɣuren d yimɣan n walma am tafsut wegṭiṭ d wumel yigran == Asedger == Tawacult-a n yimɣan tga d yiwet gar twaculin yenfufden s waṭas deg umadal yakk.
Tara, d tawsit n yimɣan anda llant wazal n 60 n telmas, Talmest ilan azal akk gar-asent d tara n tẓurin yettwaẓẓun i wakken ad tefk tiẓurin

Tifunasiyin d tawacult n tsenfednin dgi llan-t wazal n 140 n telmas n temsuṭṭad timesfenzatin, Tilmas-a llan-t s waṭas deg tiggi n tegnit, Deg telmas-is llan-t tfunasin, Amugay n waman, ulli, Amellal, amaɣaṭ d temlalt
Tiɣucaf d tawacult n tzutar yeṭṭafaren timraradin, Tawacult-a dges snat n adu-twaculin, Yiwet d adu-twacult n uɣucaf, Tis snat d Tigavyalidin dgi llan-t azal n 15 n tewsitin
Tiqerɣenbubin d tafesna n temraradin anda llant snat Kan n telmas ttidirent deg tmurt n Nyuzilanda.
Tazelmuyt d tawsit n temraradin yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tzelmay deg tfesna n tmeskebrin.
Meckenṭed d tawsit n yigṭaṭ yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tmeckunṭad.
Itbir neɣ Atbir d tawsit n iylalen yettidiren deg waṭas n yidgan dges tagrawt n tetbirin s wadduden yemgaraden seg tlemmast ar tmeqrant
Amenteẓẓa d tawsit n temsuṭaṭ yeṭṭafaren tawacult imenteẓẓaten deg tfesna n tmenteẓẓatin
Imcac d tawsit n tserɣuda yellan s ddaw n tdu-twacult n tserɣudt deg telmas-is yella wemcic amegrud d telmas is-d-yettilin
Acebcal azunɣid d talmest n temsiffatin yeṭṭafaren tawsit n tefrirut tamufayt deg twacult n icebcalen
Tikilsa, d yiwet n talmest n yemɣi yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tkilsatin, Tettwassen s ttut.
Imesminqeṛ d tawsit n yigṭaṭ yeṭṭafaren tawacult n tmesmineqṛin.Tilmas n tewsit-a d tid-ak yettidiren deg yakk tamiwin n Uruppa d Tferka d Asya, yerna tuget deg-sent ttidirent deg tẓegwa.
Waḥrir d tawsit n Imɣi seg twacult n Papaveraceae.
Anziḍ d aɣersiw yeṭṭafaren asmil n temsutad akk d tfesna n temseɣẓaẓ, Dɣa amur ameqran n tudert-is yettidir-it deg waddagen, asallaf-is d aɣezfan yeččur, al imeẓẓuɣen-is zzin.
Tuccanin d tawsit n yemɣi seg twacult n solanaceae.
Aẓerẓur neɣ imesfer d tawsit n yigṭaṭ yeṭṭafaren tawacult n temsefrin.
